---

<BaseLayout
  title="Emergency Plumber Bristol | 24/7 Plumbing Services | Call Now"
  description="Bristol's trusted emergency plumber available 24/7. Fast response for burst pipes, boiler breakdowns, blocked drains and all plumbing emergencies. Call now for immediate assistance."
  canonical="https://bristolemergencyplumber.co.uk/"
  ogTitle="Emergency Plumber Bristol | 24/7 Plumbing Services"
  ogDescription="Bristol's most trusted emergency plumber. Available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week for all plumbing emergencies."
  keywords="emergency plumber Bristol, 24 hour plumber Bristol, burst pipe repair Bristol, boiler repair Bristol, blocked drains Bristol"
  currentPage="home"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
  <link slot="extraHead" rel="preload" as="image" href="/assets/images/hero-emergency-plumber-bristol.webp" type="image/webp">

  <main id="main-content" role="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="urgency-badge"><span class="urgency-dot"></span> Engineers available now</span>
            <h1>Bristol's Trusted Emergency Plumbing Service</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Fast, Reliable 24/7 Plumbing Services Across Bristol</p>
            <p class="hero-text">When plumbing disasters strike, our experienced emergency plumbers are available around the clock across Bristol and surrounding areas.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
              <a href="tel:+441174280200" class="btn btn-phone-hero"><span class="phone-icon">&#9742;</span> Call Now: 0117 428 0200</a>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-signals">
              <span>&#10003; 30-60 Min Response</span>
              <span>&#10003; Gas Safe Registered</span>
              <span>&#10003; No Call-Out Fee</span>
              <span>&#10003; Fixed Price Quotes</span>
            </div>
            <div class="review-strip">
              <span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
              <span class="review-text">4.9/5 from 120+ Google Reviews</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-form-wrapper">
            <form class="hero-form" id="heroContactForm" aria-label="Request a callback">
              <h2>Not urgent? Request a callback</h2>
              <p>We'll get back to you within 30 minutes</p>
              <input type="text" name="website" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="hero-name">Your Name *</label>
                <input type="text" id="hero-name" name="name" required placeholder="John Smith">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="hero-phone">Phone Number *</label>
                <input type="tel" id="hero-phone" name="phone" required placeholder="07700 900000">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="hero-service">Service Required</label>
                <select id="hero-service" name="service">
                  <option value="">Please select...</option>
                  <option value="emergency">Emergency Plumber</option>
                  <option value="boiler">Boiler Repair</option>
                  <option value="drains">Blocked Drains</option>
                  <option value="general">General Plumbing</option>
                  <option value="quote">Request a Quote</option>
                  <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div id="hero-form-message" style="display: none; padding: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 0.9rem;"></div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Request Callback</button>
              <p class="hero-form-note">Or <a href="tel:+441174280200">call us now</a> for immediate help</p>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-overview">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Emergency Plumbing Services in Bristol</h2>
        <p>Comprehensive emergency plumbing solutions throughout Bristol. Our qualified team handles everything from minor leaks to major emergencies.</p>

        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon">&#128295;</span>
            <h3><a href="/emergency-plumber-bristol">Emergency Plumber Bristol</a></h3>
            <p>Immediate 24/7 response for burst pipes, flooding, gas leaks and all urgent plumbing emergencies across Bristol.</p>
            <a href="/emergency-plumber-bristol" class="read-more">Learn more &#8594;</a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon">&#128336;</span>
            <h3><a href="/24-hour-plumber-bristol">24 Hour Plumber Bristol</a></h3>
            <p>Round-the-clock plumbing help whenever you need it. Fully stocked vans for first-visit fixes, day or night.</p>
            <a href="/24-hour-plumber-bristol" class="read-more">Learn more &#8594;</a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon">&#128293;</span>
            <h3><a href="/boiler-repair-bristol">Boiler Repair Bristol</a></h3>
            <p>Gas Safe registered engineers for all boiler makes and models. Fast diagnosis and repair to restore your heating.</p>
            <a href="/boiler-repair-bristol" class="read-more">Learn more &#8594;</a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon">&#128703;</span>
            <h3><a href="/blocked-drains-bristol">Blocked Drains Bristol</a></h3>
            <p>Professional drain unblocking with high-pressure jetting and CCTV surveys. Fast, effective clearance guaranteed.</p>
            <a href="/blocked-drains-bristol" class="read-more">Learn more &#8594;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="reviews-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What Bristol Says About Us</h2>
        <div class="reviews-aggregate">
          <span class="reviews-score">4.9</span>
          <div class="reviews-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
          <p>Based on 120+ Google reviews</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reviews-grid">
          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-card-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <blockquote>"Had a burst pipe at 2am and they were here within 40 minutes. Professional, friendly, and fixed everything quickly. Can't recommend them enough."</blockquote>
