            <div class="review-card-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <blockquote>"Blocked drain was causing a terrible smell. Their team used CCTV to find the problem and cleared it in no time. Very impressed with the service."</blockquote>
            <div class="reviewer">
