      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-choose-us">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why Bristol Trusts Us for Emergency Plumbing</h2>
        <p>Over fifteen years of delivering fast, professional plumbing services at fair prices across Bristol.</p>

        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>Rapid Response Times</h3>
            <p>Our emergency plumbers reach most Bristol locations within 30-60 minutes. The nearest available plumber is always dispatched to you.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>Transparent Pricing</h3>
            <p>Clear, written quotes before any work begins. No call-out fees, no hidden charges — the price we quote is the price you pay.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit">
            <h3>Qualified Professionals</h3>
            <p>Fully qualified, Gas Safe registered, insured, and background-checked. Ongoing training keeps our team at the top of their field.</p>
          </div>

