            <h3>Guaranteed Workmanship</h3>
            <p>Every job backed by our comprehensive workmanship guarantee. If issues arise, we return to fix them at no extra cost.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="locations-served">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Locations We Serve Across Bristol</h2>
        <p>Our emergency plumbing services extend throughout Bristol and the surrounding region. We've built a network of local plumbers who know their communities inside out, ensuring rapid response times no matter where you're located.</p>

        <div class="locations-grid">
          <a href="/locations/north-bristol" class="location-link">North Bristol</a>
          <a href="/locations/south-bristol" class="location-link">South Bristol</a>
          <a href="/locations/east-bristol" class="location-link">East Bristol</a>
          <a href="/locations/west-bristol" class="location-link">West Bristol</a>
          <a href="/locations/central-bristol" class="location-link">Central Bristol</a>
        </div>

        <p class="locations-note">Covering all Bristol postcodes including BS1-BS16, BS32 and BS34. <a href="/locations/">View all areas</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How quickly can you respond to a plumbing emergency in Bristol?</h3>
            <p>We aim to reach most Bristol locations within 30-60 minutes of your call. Our emergency plumbers are strategically located across Bristol to ensure the fastest possible response times. During peak periods, we'll always give you an honest estimate of our arrival time.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you charge extra for emergency callouts at night or weekends?</h3>
            <p>Our rates remain competitive regardless of when you call. While emergency callouts may have different pricing to standard appointments, we always provide transparent quotes before beginning any work. You'll never face unexpected charges on your bill.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Are your plumbers Gas Safe registered?</h3>
            <p>Yes, all our plumbers who work on gas appliances are fully Gas Safe registered. We can provide registration details upon request for complete peace of mind. Safety is our absolute priority on every job we undertake.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What should I do while waiting for the emergency plumber?</h3>
            <p>If you have a water leak, locate your stopcock and turn off the water supply to prevent further damage. For gas-related emergencies, turn off the gas at the meter if safe to do so and open windows for ventilation. Our phone team can provide specific guidance based on your situation.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you provide written quotes before starting work?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. We always provide a clear, written quote before commencing any work. This quote will detail the work required, all costs involved, and the expected timeframe. We won't start work until you've approved the quote and you understand exactly what you're paying for.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need an Emergency Plumber in Bristol?</h2>
        <p>Don't let a plumbing emergency cause more damage to your property. Our expert team is standing by 24/7, ready to help.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="tel:+441174280200" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Call Now: 0117 428 0200</a>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">Available 24/7 including bank holidays</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    // Hero form submission
    const heroForm = document.getElementById('heroContactForm');
    const heroFormMessage = document.getElementById('hero-form-message');

    heroForm.addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();

        const submitButton = heroForm.querySelector('button[type="submit"]');
        const originalButtonText = submitButton.textContent;
        submitButton.textContent = 'Sending...';
        submitButton.disabled = true;

        const formData = new FormData(heroForm);
        const payload = {
            name: formData.get('name'),
            phone: formData.get('phone'),
            service: formData.get('service'),
            website: formData.get('website'),
            source_page: window.location.pathname
        };

        try {
            const response = await fetch('/api/leads', {
                method: 'POST',
                body: JSON.stringify(payload),
                headers: {
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                    'Accept': 'application/json'
                }
            });

            if (response.ok) {
                heroFormMessage.style.display = 'block';
                heroFormMessage.style.backgroundColor = '#d4edda';
                heroFormMessage.style.color = '#155724';
                heroFormMessage.style.border = '1px solid #c3e6cb';
                heroFormMessage.textContent = 'Thank you! We\'ll call you back shortly.';
                heroForm.reset();
            } else {
                const data = await response.json().catch(() => ({}));
                throw new Error(data.message || 'Form submission failed');
            }
        } catch (error) {
            heroFormMessage.style.display = 'block';
            heroFormMessage.style.backgroundColor = '#f8d7da';
            heroFormMessage.style.color = '#721c24';
            heroFormMessage.style.border = '1px solid #f5c6cb';
            heroFormMessage.textContent = 'Sorry, there was an error. Please call us directly at 0117 428 0200.';
        } finally {
            submitButton.textContent = originalButtonText;
            submitButton.disabled = false;
        }
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
